Convert the following markdown-formatted curriculum into a structured JSON format:
{{markdown_text}}
If the input is 
- Topic: 
  - Subtopic 1
  - Subtopic 2
  - Subtopic 3

The desired JSON structure is: 
[{"topic": "topicName", "subtopics": ["subtopic 1", "subtopic 2", "subtopic 3", "Sub Subtopic 1"]}, 
{"topic": "topicName", "subtopics": ["subtopic 1", "subtopic 2", "subtopic 3"]}]
The subtopics list should be flat, not nested. Only give the JSON structure and nothing else. It should be directly parsable.